file: crates/ctx-core/src/lib.rs
behavior: Crate root that re-exports the shared access-gate module as the single dependency-free source of truth for secret-denylist logic across CTX crates.
edit_notes:
  - Access gate logic must not be duplicated in ctx-access or ctx-summarize; a divergent denylist is treated as a security bug (DECISIONS ADR-023).
  - Each consumer crate maps the neutral deny reason from access into its own typed error; do not add crate-specific error types here.
functions:
invariants:
  - Crate has no dependencies; logic here must remain dependency-free.
external_deps: